                Everything.me
              </h1>
              <h2 class="project-tags">
                Group project &nbsp; Recommendation systems &nbsp; Desktop only &nbsp; Ruby on Rails
              </h2>
              <p class="project-description">
                Everything is the final project I developed with 3 other students in Le Wagon. Everything gathers info about your tastes in a fun way, and gives movie recommendations based on your similarity with your friends and other users.
