                Group project &nbsp; Multiplayer game &nbsp; Desktop only &nbsp; Ruby on Rails
              </h2>
              <p class="project-description" style="color: rgba(240,240,240,1)">
                Le Wagon asked us to build something with a marketplace. My group went a little further. We built a game in which you start with a spaceship and can choose parts for the spaceship. Then, you make expeditions to look for better parts and you can trade parts in the galactic marketplace. At the end of each day, a race takes plays to find the best pilot of the galaxy. All of that was developed in 5 days!
              </p>
              <p class="project-cta">
                Click to see details
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <% project_no += 1 %>

