              <p class="project-description">
                I created Burger Shop because I wanted to practice Rails and MVC architecture on a higher level. In Burger Shop, you can shop for burgers and beverages from many options. All burgers are 100% customizable. You can manage addresses for the delivery and track the progress of your delivery.
