                Senior project: Neural networks applied to Football
              </h1>
              <h2 class="project-tags">
                Academic publication &nbsp; Neural Networks &nbsp; Matlab
              </h2>
              <p class="project-description">
                I always thought that end of course research projects have boring titles and for many it is boring work you have to do just to graduate. I wanted to spice it up a little bit. I tried to study how well neural networks can predict soccer matches and devise a bot which is able to profit in sports bets. In the end, the bots made a small profit on average, but were unreliable. However, the process and results brought a lot of cool insights, analysis and graphs.
              </p>
              <p class="project-cta">
                Click to download article (pt-br)
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

