                Blackjack analysis
              </h1>
              <h2 class="project-tags">
                Curiosity project &nbsp; Statistical analysis &nbsp; C
              </h2>
              <p class="project-description">
                I always found the dynamics and mathematics behind the games interesting. Blackjack caught my attention because it is the fairest game that can be played on a casino, and the only game in which a player can be skilled enough to actually beat the house. Back when I was 14, I wrote these codes in C to make a statistic analysis of the game and built a full report that has been downloaded over 500 times!
              </p>
              <p class="project-cta">
                Click to see details
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</div>


